data.description: This 3-bedroom, 1-bath gem in Houston, TX is a must-see! Step inside to find a beautifully updated kitchen with modern appliances and stunning flooring throughout the house (no carpet!). But that's not all – the real showstopper is the massive backyard. Imagine all the possibilities with a spacious slab and utility connections ready for your dream project. But here's the icing on the cake – there's also a garage that offers flexibility. You can convert it into a fourth bedroom for extra space or even a convenient additional bathroom.
